channel.description:
Ok, I made all these for guys on another forum. Ive been following this one tut and it has greatly inproved me. If you want the tut, just PM me and Ill send you the URL. Anyways, Im going to place them in order from best to worst. I hope you guys enjoy the show.
BEST- [img]http://i225.photobucket.com/albums/dd111/manofwar012/LEO.jpg[/img] V2- [IMG]http://i225.photobucket.com/albums/dd111/manofwar012/Manofwar12/LEOv2.jpg[/img]
2nd BEST- [img]http://i225.photobucket.com/albums/dd111/manofwar012/Ladypk.jpg[/img]
3rd BEST- [img]http://i225.photobucket.com/albums/dd111/manofwar012/FrozenAge.jpg[/img]
I spent about 3 hours total on these, so I guess 1 hour each. I worked real hard and Ive improved.
Please tell me what you think.
~Tst1
